went here in late summer on a weekday and it was fantastic GOODREVIEW pamela s and deluca s go back and forth in battle for best GOODREVIEW breakfast in the city there s not much to this place just a simple diner but the food is out of this world i had a bacon cheese omelette the wife had french toast and my son had the short stack of pancakes with two coffees and a chocolate milk the bill came to 31 00 it s a cash only establishment so be prepared we ll be back
